subject: Basketball

Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Brittney Griner scored 17 of her 26 points in the second half Sunday as the top-ranked Lady Bears pulled out a 76-67 victory against the No. 6 Lady Volunteers in Knoxville, Tenn.
